{
  "stem": "20710.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was the mother and sisters of this man who took me out from the-- from the bunker the time to the ghetto that he was a part of, the Judenfrei.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was the-- his mother and his two sisters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One was my age.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One was a little bit younger, a couple years younger.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, and that's-- [SIGHS] that's what I-- I think this was until the end.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we were in the forest, and the same thing, you know-- frightened, running, running-- until-- until they came in July-- what was it, in July, when-- when-- when the Russians-- when the Germans started pulling back?",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "June, July?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of which year?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of '44.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were up there in the-- in the forest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a lot of forest, a very lot of forestry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were there and we were up-- you know, there were hills.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were going up on the hills to see what's going on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because next to the forest was a lot of fields and there was a road.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we wanted to see because we could hear, you know, planes and shooting and all.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We knew a war is going on, but we didn't know who is where and what.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we went up to the-- on these hills and to see what's going on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we could see, you know, soldiers and tanks, you know, moving, forward, backward.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we didn't know if this is German or they are-- they're-- they are Russians.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
